message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - This paper deals with machine learning models for MRI image segmentation, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. The use of sequential structure and the proposed hybrid forest algorithm also suggest a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NEURON). Additionally, the application of the method to left ventricle segmentation in medical imaging indicates a potential fit for the medical imaging (cs.MED) category.
